# 🟡 MEDIUM — Should Fix

---

### MED-01 · Student dashboard scans ALL attendance records (no batch filter)

**File**: [student/dashboard/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/dashboard/route.ts#L35-L37)

```typescript
const attendanceRecords = await Attendance.find({
    'records.student': studentId
}).lean();
```

**What**: Queries ALL attendance documents containing this student. With 1000 attendance sessions, this becomes a full collection scan.

**Fix**: Add batch filter and date range:
```typescript
const attendanceRecords = await Attendance.find({
    'records.student': studentId,
    batch: student.batch,
}).lean();
```

---

### MED-02 · Admin users GET returns ALL users without pagination

**File**: [admin/users/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/users/route.ts#L24)

```typescript
const users = await User.find({}).select('-password')...
```

**What**: No `skip`/`limit` pagination. At 1000 users, this returns a large JSON payload.

**Contrast**: [admin/students/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/students/route.ts) ✅ already has pagination.

