### MED-03 · `admin/settings` PATCH — no input length sanitization

**File**: [admin/settings/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/settings/route.ts#L37)

```typescript
if (body.collegeName !== undefined) settings.collegeName = body.collegeName;
```

**What**: `collegeName` is saved as-is. No length cap, no trim. Someone could set it to a 10MB string.

