### MED-05 · Student attendance `self-mark` needs batch check before teacher query

**File**: [student/attendance/self-mark/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/attendance/self-mark/route.ts)

**What**: The batch verification queries the [User](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/User.ts#5-35) model separately. If the attendance has no `batch` field set (old records), the check is skipped, potentially allowing cross-batch attendance marking.

