### MED-07 · Finance dashboard has no try-catch

**File**: [admin/finance/dashboard/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/finance/dashboard/route.ts)

**What**: Aggregation queries can fail. No error handling wrapping the dashboard GET.

