| 🟡 MEDIUM | 10 | Full collection scans, no pagination, missing indexes, raw JSON parsing, status bypass |
| 🟢 LOW | 7 | Inconsistent bcrypt rounds, missing try-catch, OTP cleanup, sequential uploads |

**Total issues found: 29**

