# Recommended Fix Order

1. **CRIT-02** — Rate limit login (5 min fix, highest ROI)
2. **CRIT-03** — `crypto.randomInt` for OTP (1 line change)
3. **CRIT-01** — Escape regex inputs (2 line change)
4. **CRIT-05** — Remove error.message from responses (grep + replace)
5. **CRIT-04** — Verify OTP before registration
6. **HIGH-04** — Security headers in next.config (copy-paste)
7. **HIGH-01** — Teacher attendance ownership check (1 line)
8. **HIGH-02** — Teacher test ownership check (2 lines)
9. **HIGH-06** — AuditLog on user CRUD (copy pattern from salary)
10. **HIGH-05** — Stronger password policy
11. **MED-10** — Database indexes (schema changes)
12. Rest by priority
